1
00:01:19,370 --> 00:01:27,370
(THE SPIREALM)

2
00:01:30,340 --> 00:01:32,070
(Episode 8)

3
00:01:33,229 --> 00:01:36,110
Was Ruan the only person who came out of the 10th door?

4
00:01:36,110 --> 00:01:37,190
And a woman.

5
00:01:37,830 --> 00:01:39,160
She's quite something.

6
00:01:39,670 --> 00:01:41,430
The one who can pass through the 10th door

7
00:01:41,430 --> 00:01:43,560
is definitely not an ordinary person.

8
00:01:46,270 --> 00:01:48,310
Did you get the clue for the fifth door?

9
00:01:48,310 --> 00:01:49,310
Yes.

10
00:01:54,130 --> 00:01:55,450
(Human Skin Drum)

11
00:01:56,430 --> 00:01:57,870
Human skin drum.

12
00:01:59,590 --> 00:02:01,070
Human skin drum?

13
00:02:02,430 --> 00:02:03,760
Is it a musical instrument?

14
00:02:03,760 --> 00:02:05,430
The human skin drum

15
00:02:05,670 --> 00:02:06,750
is a legend.

16
00:02:07,350 --> 00:02:10,810
It's a story about a girl looking for her missing older sister.

17
00:02:12,910 --> 00:02:13,790
And then?

18
00:02:13,790 --> 00:02:15,750
Of course, there's something else.

19
00:02:15,750 --> 00:02:16,750
I...

20
00:02:17,350 --> 00:02:19,310
I haven't had a chance to search yet.

21
00:02:19,310 --> 00:02:19,990
When you are facing trouble,

22
00:02:19,990 --> 00:02:21,550
it would be nice if you could remain this calm.

23
00:02:21,550 --> 00:02:22,950
What are you talking about?

24
00:02:22,950 --> 00:02:24,680
I haven't entered the door yet.

25
00:02:26,150 --> 00:02:27,610
Hurry up and figure it out.

26
00:02:29,070 --> 00:02:30,270
You're slow-witted.

27
00:02:30,510 --> 00:02:32,190
The door should arrive in half a day.

28
00:02:32,190 --> 00:02:33,590
Don't make any mistakes.

29
00:02:33,829 --> 00:02:34,829
Yes.

30
00:02:43,150 --> 00:02:44,150
What did you find?

31
00:02:46,990 --> 00:02:49,310
This is an ancient legend.

32
00:02:49,740 --> 00:02:52,510
In some places, people flay the skin of virgins

33
00:02:52,510 --> 00:02:53,570
to make drumheads.

34
00:02:54,070 --> 00:02:55,990
It is said that the sound produced by such drums

35
00:02:55,990 --> 00:02:59,250
can connect life and death, transcending reincarnation.

36
00:02:59,390 --> 00:03:02,230
In the legend, a girl was chosen to be made into a drum.

37
00:03:02,230 --> 00:03:05,270
Her older sister volunteered to become a human skin drum to save her.

38
00:03:05,270 --> 00:03:07,150
She was looking for her missing sister

39
00:03:07,150 --> 00:03:09,070
but couldn't find her for a long time

40
00:03:09,070 --> 00:03:12,330
until she heard the drum sound coming from the distant sky.

41
00:03:13,510 --> 00:03:14,590
Ancient legend.

42
00:03:15,150 --> 00:03:16,950
It's filled with superstition.

43
00:03:20,270 --> 00:03:21,270
Are you tired?

44
00:03:23,510 --> 00:03:24,510
I'm fine.

45
00:03:24,750 --> 00:03:26,590
Ruan, don't worry.

46
00:03:27,070 --> 00:03:28,870
I can bring them back safely.

47
00:03:30,230 --> 00:03:32,090
Let me take them to pass this door.

48
00:03:32,630 --> 00:03:33,829
Let me think about it.

49
00:03:36,590 --> 00:03:37,590
I don't agree.

50
00:03:47,510 --> 00:03:48,510
Why are you here?

51
00:03:51,350 --> 00:03:52,350
I need you.

52
00:03:56,510 --> 00:03:57,510
What do you mean?

53
00:03:59,270 --> 00:04:00,400
I mean it literally.

54
00:04:01,950 --> 00:04:03,210
I mean, you cannot die.

55
00:04:05,310 --> 00:04:07,790
You can make it clearer.

56
00:04:14,550 --> 00:04:15,550
This is for you.

57
00:04:21,390 --> 00:04:22,390
Some people

58
00:04:23,190 --> 00:04:25,050
are naturally meant for the door.

59
00:04:43,909 --> 00:04:45,230
Qianli, what's wrong?

60
00:04:45,550 --> 00:04:46,550
What's wrong?

61
00:04:50,430 --> 00:04:52,040
Why are you watching this late at night?

62
00:04:52,040 --> 00:04:52,710
Aren't you scared?

63
00:04:52,710 --> 00:04:53,870
Aren't you scared?

64
00:04:54,030 --> 00:04:55,350
No, I'm not.

65
00:04:58,350 --> 00:04:59,350
Don't...

66
00:04:59,350 --> 00:05:00,350
I can't breathe.

67
00:05:02,470 --> 00:05:04,230
Let me hold you. Let me hold you.

68
00:05:06,390 --> 00:05:09,110
Lingling, you are really a good person.

69
00:05:09,590 --> 00:05:10,950
I think so too.

70
00:05:18,150 --> 00:05:18,870
Green ghost!

71
00:05:18,870 --> 00:05:20,550
You two are making a fuss in the middle of the night.

72
00:05:20,550 --> 00:05:21,810
How could I go to sleep?

73
00:05:22,230 --> 00:05:23,980
Don't watch horror movies if you're afraid.

74
00:05:23,980 --> 00:05:25,910
Even a ghost would be scared of you.

75
00:05:26,670 --> 00:05:27,930
If I don't watch it now,

76
00:05:28,190 --> 00:05:29,550
I'll go inside the door.

77
00:05:30,150 --> 00:05:31,590
Then you can scream inside the door.

78
00:05:31,590 --> 00:05:33,650
You may scare the Door Ghost to death.

79
00:05:34,380 --> 00:05:36,040
I'm screaming for you to hear.

80
00:05:37,990 --> 00:05:40,270
Cheng Yixie, come and discipline your brother.

81
00:05:40,270 --> 00:05:41,930
He's disturbing people here.

82
00:05:47,870 --> 00:05:50,510
If you speak one more word tonight,

83
00:05:51,590 --> 00:05:53,920
you'll go inside the next door on your own.

84
00:05:57,630 --> 00:05:59,790
Lingling, don't watch horror movies with him.

85
00:05:59,790 --> 00:06:00,830
It's too scary.

86
00:06:01,070 --> 00:06:03,070
It damages your hearing and health.

87
00:06:05,110 --> 00:06:06,110
It's not scary.

88
00:06:14,470 --> 00:06:15,930
Do you still want to watch?

89
00:06:18,790 --> 00:06:20,520
You're really not gonna speak?

90
00:06:20,670 --> 00:06:22,000
Your brother is joking.

91
00:06:25,430 --> 00:06:26,430
Sit.

92
00:06:35,830 --> 00:06:37,890
Your body isn't fully recovered yet.

93
00:06:37,909 --> 00:06:39,630
Why are you going inside the door?

94
00:06:39,630 --> 00:06:41,230
I can totally handle it.

95
00:06:41,590 --> 00:06:42,590
I'm worried.

96
00:06:47,030 --> 00:06:48,690
If Ling Jiushi were not there,

97
00:06:49,550 --> 00:06:51,390
would you still insist on leading the team?

98
00:06:51,390 --> 00:06:52,390
No.

99
00:06:52,620 --> 00:06:54,620
What's so special about him anyway?

100
00:06:57,070 --> 00:06:58,670
That's none of your concern.

101
00:07:00,790 --> 00:07:02,830
He wants to save the patriarch's daughter.

102
00:07:02,830 --> 00:07:06,560
He wants to save the Wizard. If it were me, I wouldn't care about him.

103
00:07:07,360 --> 00:07:10,830
So, I have to lead the team.

104
00:07:11,190 --> 00:07:13,390
Are you choosing him to be your partner?

105
00:07:14,230 --> 00:07:16,290
You're not satisfied with Yi Manman?

106
00:07:17,750 --> 00:07:20,010
Why are you suddenly interested in this?

107
00:07:20,510 --> 00:07:22,040
If you want to be my partner,

108
00:07:22,950 --> 00:07:23,990
I'll consider it.

109
00:07:24,270 --> 00:07:25,270
Thanks.

110
00:07:26,230 --> 00:07:28,430
I just want to protect my silly brother.

111
00:07:37,750 --> 00:07:38,750
Just say it.

112
00:07:39,310 --> 00:07:40,170
It's nonsense.

113
00:07:40,310 --> 00:07:41,310
Go ahead.

114
00:07:45,030 --> 00:07:46,430
Take good care of Qianli.

115
00:07:46,550 --> 00:07:47,950
Nonsense. I surely will.

116
00:07:52,670 --> 00:07:53,670
So,

117
00:07:53,950 --> 00:07:56,270
the landlady is Jiu's mother?

118
00:07:58,230 --> 00:08:00,160
Is she a good person or a bad person?

119
00:08:01,110 --> 00:08:02,310
In this world,

120
00:08:02,430 --> 00:08:05,190
purely good or bad are both rare.

121
00:08:11,180 --> 00:08:13,070
I'll take you to pass the door this time.

122
00:08:13,070 --> 00:08:14,070
Great!

123
00:08:14,870 --> 00:08:16,070
Can your body take it?

124
00:08:17,070 --> 00:08:18,070
I'm fine now.

125
00:08:21,950 --> 00:08:22,950
Wear this.

126
00:08:23,150 --> 00:08:24,880
Take it off as soon as you get in.

127
00:08:26,310 --> 00:08:27,310
Go get changed.

128
00:08:27,430 --> 00:08:28,430
Okay.

129
00:08:50,270 --> 00:08:51,270
Coming.

130
00:08:52,310 --> 00:08:53,310
Let's go.

131
00:09:56,110 --> 00:09:57,640
How did I bring this with me?

132
00:10:12,110 --> 00:10:13,110
Where are they?

133
00:10:19,830 --> 00:10:20,830
Don't.

134
00:10:21,150 --> 00:10:22,150
Don't hit me.

135
00:10:23,230 --> 00:10:24,230
Who are you?

136
00:10:24,870 --> 00:10:25,870
Where am I?

137
00:10:26,630 --> 00:10:27,670
I'm so scared.

138
00:10:28,270 --> 00:10:29,270
Look.

139
00:10:29,630 --> 00:10:30,910
You're hitting me.

140
00:10:30,910 --> 00:10:32,170
What are you afraid of?

141
00:10:37,350 --> 00:10:38,350
Hui.

142
00:10:40,350 --> 00:10:41,590
Hui, you're not dead.

143
00:10:43,030 --> 00:10:44,550
I've been waiting for you.

144
00:10:46,150 --> 00:10:47,150
Who is Hui?

145
00:10:48,030 --> 00:10:49,230
Do we know each other?

146
00:10:55,350 --> 00:10:56,150
I'm sorry.

147
00:10:56,150 --> 00:10:58,150
I... I mistook you for someone else.

148
00:11:00,270 --> 00:11:01,730
You just came here, right?

149
00:11:03,430 --> 00:11:04,490
It's getting dark.

150
00:11:05,270 --> 00:11:06,630
We need to go to the destination now.

151
00:11:06,630 --> 00:11:07,630
Destination?

152
00:11:08,030 --> 00:11:09,150
Who are you?

153
00:11:09,870 --> 00:11:10,870
Where is this?

154
00:11:12,120 --> 00:11:13,120
Is this...

155
00:11:16,790 --> 00:11:17,790
a kaleidoscope?

156
00:11:20,030 --> 00:11:21,630
I don't know if it was broken.

157
00:11:21,910 --> 00:11:24,510
It's someone else's stuff. I have to return it.

158
00:11:25,470 --> 00:11:26,670
Let's talk on the way.

159
00:11:42,110 --> 00:11:43,110
Well,

160
00:11:43,670 --> 00:11:45,790
I'm Yu Lingling. What about you?

161
00:11:46,670 --> 00:11:47,670
I'm Xu Jin.

162
00:11:50,150 --> 00:11:52,710
How did you start playing the game, Spi Realm?

163
00:11:53,310 --> 00:11:55,830
Game? What game?

164
00:11:57,720 --> 00:11:59,350
Maybe you accidentally opened it,

165
00:11:59,350 --> 00:12:00,480
and you didn't know.

166
00:12:01,470 --> 00:12:02,630
This is a game?

167
00:12:04,910 --> 00:12:06,350
There are 12 doors in total.

168
00:12:06,350 --> 00:12:07,550
You have to clear the game

169
00:12:07,550 --> 00:12:09,080
before you can get rid of it.

170
00:12:09,910 --> 00:12:11,030
You probably

171
00:12:11,030 --> 00:12:13,150
accidentally opened a door at home

172
00:12:13,150 --> 00:12:14,150
and ended up here.

173
00:12:14,350 --> 00:12:15,410
Do you remember it?

174
00:12:16,710 --> 00:12:17,710
I don't remember.

175
00:12:19,830 --> 00:12:20,830
It's okay.

176
00:12:21,110 --> 00:12:22,110
Just remember.

177
00:12:22,630 --> 00:12:24,390
You have to be careful here.

178
00:12:24,430 --> 00:12:26,630
Otherwise, your life will be in danger.

179
00:12:26,990 --> 00:12:28,390
My life will be in danger?

180
00:12:29,270 --> 00:12:31,670
I don't want to take risks. I want to go home.

181
00:12:31,670 --> 00:12:32,670
Don't run around.

182
00:12:33,000 --> 00:12:34,350
If you keep running like this,

183
00:12:34,350 --> 00:12:35,750
you'll be in real danger.

184
00:12:36,670 --> 00:12:37,670
Trust me.

185
00:12:38,990 --> 00:12:39,990
Hui.

186
00:12:42,350 --> 00:12:44,990
If you really want to see Hui again,

187
00:12:45,380 --> 00:12:46,640
you have to stay alive.

188
00:12:50,110 --> 00:12:51,470
That should be the village.

189
00:12:51,470 --> 00:12:53,600
Let's go there and join the others.

190
00:12:55,110 --> 00:12:56,110
Let's go.

191
00:13:03,750 --> 00:13:06,670
Attention, late tourists, please hurry up.

192
00:13:08,070 --> 00:13:09,360
Who is she?

193
00:13:10,380 --> 00:13:11,710
She's an NPC in the game.

194
00:13:12,630 --> 00:13:14,030
What is an NPC?

195
00:13:15,190 --> 00:13:16,190
I won't explain.

196
00:13:16,390 --> 00:13:17,070
Let's go inside first.

197
00:13:17,070 --> 00:13:18,070
Okay.

198
00:13:23,190 --> 00:13:25,230
Say something. Where are we?

199
00:13:25,350 --> 00:13:27,590
I... I'm telling you, don't lie to me.

200
00:13:27,590 --> 00:13:28,990
I've already called the police.

201
00:13:28,990 --> 00:13:30,390
The police are on the way.

202
00:13:30,590 --> 00:13:31,590
It's okay.

203
00:13:32,070 --> 00:13:34,110
He should be a newcomer like you.

204
00:13:34,360 --> 00:13:35,470
Do you... Do you know where this is?

205
00:13:35,470 --> 00:13:36,470
Let's go.

206
00:13:36,710 --> 00:13:37,720
Please come in.

207
00:13:37,720 --> 00:13:39,310
I was playing games at home,

208
00:13:39,340 --> 00:13:40,350
and I was about to achieve a pentakill.

209
00:13:40,350 --> 00:13:41,010
How did I...

210
00:13:41,080 --> 00:13:42,110
How did I come here

211
00:13:42,110 --> 00:13:43,470
with a swoosh?

212
00:13:45,110 --> 00:13:47,110
Tell me where this place is.

213
00:13:49,230 --> 00:13:50,470
Can you shut up?

214
00:13:52,110 --> 00:13:54,770
I've been listening to your nagging all the way.

215
00:13:55,230 --> 00:13:56,230
If you are able,

216
00:13:56,590 --> 00:13:58,520
find a way to clear this and get out.

217
00:13:59,590 --> 00:14:00,950
If you think you can't do it,

218
00:14:00,950 --> 00:14:02,480
just shut up and wait to die.

219
00:14:02,720 --> 00:14:03,830
Do you understand?

220
00:14:03,870 --> 00:14:05,540
There are quite a few people here, twelve in total.

221
00:14:05,540 --> 00:14:06,590
I'm going out now.

222
00:14:06,950 --> 00:14:08,750
I will definitely find a way out.

223
00:14:09,700 --> 00:14:11,190
Hey. Friend.

224
00:14:11,230 --> 00:14:12,190
Don't.

225
00:14:12,190 --> 00:14:13,470
It might be safer here.

226
00:14:13,550 --> 00:14:14,480
Calm down.

227
00:14:14,480 --> 00:14:15,480
Safe?

228
00:14:16,070 --> 00:14:17,930
Where did this nice guy come from?

229
00:14:18,590 --> 00:14:19,990
You're so kind

230
00:14:20,100 --> 00:14:21,470
and good at comforting people.

231
00:14:21,470 --> 00:14:23,230
Why don't you help him clear the game

232
00:14:23,230 --> 00:14:24,230
and save his life?

233
00:14:24,470 --> 00:14:25,200
Will you?

234
00:14:25,200 --> 00:14:26,460
It's okay. Have a seat.

235
00:14:27,070 --> 00:14:28,110
How rude.

236
00:14:31,390 --> 00:14:32,390
What did you say?

237
00:14:34,590 --> 00:14:37,350
Is it polite to say that in front of me?

238
00:14:37,750 --> 00:14:38,750
Friend.

239
00:14:39,870 --> 00:14:41,800
You don't have to be so aggressive.

240
00:14:42,390 --> 00:14:43,910
Don't touch me.

241
00:14:45,140 --> 00:14:46,140
What?

242
00:14:47,750 --> 00:14:48,750
You want a fight?

243
00:14:50,350 --> 00:14:51,350
Come on.

244
00:14:52,510 --> 00:14:54,840
I'll let you start first with three moves.

245
00:14:55,390 --> 00:14:56,390
Come on.

246
00:15:01,270 --> 00:15:02,270
Friend.

247
00:15:03,030 --> 00:15:04,150
You're so young.

248
00:15:04,630 --> 00:15:06,230
Why are you so hot-tempered?

249
00:15:06,630 --> 00:15:07,750
Who are you?

250
00:15:08,270 --> 00:15:09,270
You're together?

251
00:15:09,790 --> 00:15:10,790
Hands off me.

252
00:15:13,500 --> 00:15:15,150
What if I don't?

253
00:15:17,630 --> 00:15:18,630
Let go, let go.

254
00:15:18,740 --> 00:15:19,740
Take it easy.

255
00:15:19,870 --> 00:15:20,990
Take it easy.

256
00:15:24,980 --> 00:15:25,980
Okay.

257
00:15:27,750 --> 00:15:30,680
I'm Meng Yu, and this is my fourth time passing doors.

258
00:15:31,150 --> 00:15:33,350
I'm Yu Lingling, and it's my third time.

259
00:15:38,510 --> 00:15:39,510
Sit down.

260
00:15:40,390 --> 00:15:41,390
Let's go.

261
00:15:43,470 --> 00:15:44,730
You're quite skilled.

262
00:15:44,790 --> 00:15:47,390
Looks like my money was well spent.

263
00:15:50,390 --> 00:15:52,600
Bro, are you feeling unwell?

264
00:15:52,870 --> 00:15:53,870
Are you okay?

265
00:15:53,990 --> 00:15:54,990
I'm fine.

266
00:15:55,590 --> 00:15:57,670
I've been in poor health since I was little.

267
00:15:57,670 --> 00:15:59,070
Thanks for your concern.

268
00:15:59,630 --> 00:16:00,690
My name is Zhu Meng.

269
00:16:01,910 --> 00:16:02,910
I'm Mu Yu.

270
00:16:03,350 --> 00:16:04,350
She is Xu Jin.

271
00:16:04,470 --> 00:16:05,470
She's a newcomer.

272
00:16:07,910 --> 00:16:09,000
I asked the woman

273
00:16:09,390 --> 00:16:11,050
outside about the situation.

274
00:16:11,150 --> 00:16:13,010
She said that she was a tour guide.

275
00:16:13,380 --> 00:16:15,590
We're all here for a tour.

276
00:16:16,140 --> 00:16:17,140
Tour?

277
00:16:17,470 --> 00:16:19,510
Did she tell you when we could get out?

278
00:16:19,870 --> 00:16:20,870
No.

279
00:16:20,990 --> 00:16:23,590
She just said that we have to visit all the attractions,

280
00:16:23,590 --> 00:16:25,320
and there might be a time limit.

281
00:16:25,670 --> 00:16:27,200
It's still unclear for now.

282
00:16:27,510 --> 00:16:28,870
Where are we staying tonight?

283
00:16:28,870 --> 00:16:29,870
Right here?

284
00:16:30,870 --> 00:16:32,390
The rooms are on the second floor.

285
00:16:32,390 --> 00:16:33,790
Each room has three beds.

286
00:16:34,200 --> 00:16:35,400
Let's divide them up.

287
00:16:35,910 --> 00:16:37,440
Why don't we stay together?

