410
00:24:26,350 --> 00:24:27,350
Let's go.

411
00:24:45,870 --> 00:24:48,670
The sound seems to be coming from the second floor.

412
00:24:50,070 --> 00:24:51,230
But that's not right.

413
00:24:51,230 --> 00:24:52,950
There isn't a second floor here.

414
00:24:52,950 --> 00:24:54,610
Then, where does it come from?

415
00:24:55,870 --> 00:24:57,150
The ceiling?

416
00:24:57,150 --> 00:24:58,150
Don't look up.

417
00:24:59,190 --> 00:25:01,190
The tour guide told us not to look up.

418
00:25:01,510 --> 00:25:02,510
Oh, right.

419
00:25:14,790 --> 00:25:16,120
You've run too far away.

420
00:25:16,150 --> 00:25:18,270
Remember not to wander around anymore.

421
00:25:18,270 --> 00:25:20,270
You don't seem to care much about me.

422
00:25:20,510 --> 00:25:23,190
Don't you believe we might actually cut you out?

423
00:25:24,060 --> 00:25:25,060
I do believe it.

424
00:25:25,510 --> 00:25:26,950
This place makes me feel so depressed

425
00:25:26,950 --> 00:25:28,750
