433
00:25:52,150 --> 00:25:54,740
The painting is about two sisters playing hide-and-seek.

434
00:25:54,740 --> 00:25:56,910
The older one has gone out of sight, hiding away.

435
00:25:56,910 --> 00:25:58,840
