488
00:29:25,230 --> 00:29:27,470
That means I'm still useful, right?

489
00:29:27,470 --> 00:29:28,530
Of course, you are.

490
00:29:30,830 --> 00:29:31,830
Lingling,

491
00:29:32,190 --> 00:29:33,630
you and I will go up there,

492
00:29:33,710 --> 00:29:34,960
while Zhu Meng stays put,

493
00:29:34,960 --> 00:29:37,160
so he can notify us if anything happens.

494
00:29:37,870 --> 00:29:39,200
Kiddo, you've grown up.

495
00:29:39,470 --> 00:29:40,470
Go ahead.

496
00:30:30,110 --> 00:30:31,840
