497
00:30:44,510 --> 00:30:45,510
Are you okay?

498
00:30:47,350 --> 00:30:49,070
What happened? Did you slip?

499
00:30:49,110 --> 00:30:50,190
Someone pushed me.

500
00:30:50,630 --> 00:30:51,630
Ah?

501
00:30:52,110 --> 00:30:53,110
You were pushed?

502
00:30:55,110 --> 00:30:57,310
But there were no other people up there.

503
00:30:58,190 --> 00:30:59,190
What's wrong?

504
00:31:01,950 --> 00:31:02,950
Are you alright?

505
00:31:06,510 --> 00:31:08,270
No one else was up there, right?

506
00:31:09,470 --> 00:31:11,000
There's blood on your back.

507
00:31:11,150 --> 00:31:12,150
Huh?

508
00:31:12,910 --> 00:31:15,070
