512
00:31:31,790 --> 00:31:34,150
Would she know something about it?

513
00:31:41,150 --> 00:31:42,150
Go ask her.

514
00:31:51,750 --> 00:31:52,750
Madam,

515
00:31:53,750 --> 00:31:55,750
