558
00:34:27,150 --> 00:34:28,389
The weather is so bad.

559
00:34:28,510 --> 00:34:30,710
There's no doubt it'll rain at any time.

560
00:34:39,230 --> 00:34:40,510
Do you hear something?

561
00:34:40,790 --> 00:34:41,790
What?

562
00:34:46,909 --> 00:34:47,909
Drumbeats.

563
00:35:09,670 --> 00:35:10,670
Xu Jin,

564
00:35:11,320 --> 00:35:13,180
