565
00:35:13,840 --> 00:35:15,590
They sound horrifying.

566
00:35:21,870 --> 00:35:23,590
T-This place is so scary.

567
00:35:23,630 --> 00:35:25,030
We'd better leave now!

568
00:35:25,030 --> 00:35:26,230
Let's get out of here!

569
00:35:26,270 --> 00:35:27,270
Shut up!

570
00:35:27,550 --> 00:35:29,430
No more yelling and crying.

571
00:35:29,670 --> 00:35:33,070
The tour guide has said that no one can leave until the tour is over.

572
00:35:33,190 --> 00:35:34,510
Stop panicking, guys!

573
00:35:35,390 --> 00:35:36,270
We haven't violated any rules.

574
00:35:36,270 --> 00:35:38,150
That thing might not kill us.

575
00:35:38,470 --> 00:35:39,310
But...

576
00:35:39,310 --> 00:35:40,470
But staying here won't do us any good!

577
00:35:40,470 --> 00:35:41,470
But what?

578
00:35:42,430 --> 00:35:43,910
But what?

579
00:35:43,910 --> 00:35:46,000
What are you trying to say?

580
00:35:46,180 --> 00:35:47,630
You can either go out now

581
00:35:48,590 --> 00:35:49,950
or wait for me to throw you out!

582
00:35:49,950 --> 00:35:50,910
I'm not going out!

583
00:35:50,910 --> 00:35:51,670
I don't want to die!

584
00:35:51,670 --> 00:35:52,670
- Get out! - I won't!

585
00:35:52,670 --> 00:35:54,070
- Go! - I'm not going out!

586
00:35:54,870 --> 00:35:56,110
Coward!

587
00:35:57,310 --> 00:35:58,770
You're a bunch of cowards!

588
00:36:13,270 --> 00:36:14,270
Meng Yu!

589
00:36:29,910 --> 00:36:32,440
Something is wrong with the sound of the rain.

590
00:36:33,630 --> 00:36:34,870
Instead of rain,

591
00:36:36,870 --> 00:36:38,130
it's pouring needles.

592
00:36:42,310 --> 00:36:44,550
Do you mean this is a rain of needles?

593
00:36:47,830 --> 00:36:48,990
How come?

594
00:36:49,310 --> 00:36:50,150
Help!

595
00:36:50,150 --> 00:36:50,990
Hey!

596
00:36:50,990 --> 00:36:51,990
Help!

597
00:36:53,150 --> 00:36:54,190
Mr. Huang!

598
00:37:02,710 --> 00:37:03,910
Were you close to him?

599
00:37:05,750 --> 00:37:06,750
N-No.

600
00:37:08,150 --> 00:37:10,470
I just think he died a tragic death.

601
00:37:14,950 --> 00:37:16,780
Will we be able to leave this place?

602
00:37:16,780 --> 00:37:18,550
Will we all die outside?

603
00:37:19,750 --> 00:37:21,310
But the spot where we're supposed to meet the tour guide

604
00:37:21,310 --> 00:37:22,310
is outside.

605
00:37:22,470 --> 00:37:23,670
It's almost time.

606
00:37:23,870 --> 00:37:25,800
Are we gonna be stuck here forever?

607
00:37:36,190 --> 00:37:37,510
Dear visitors,

608
00:37:37,630 --> 00:37:39,990
the exhibition hall is about to close.

609
00:37:40,150 --> 00:37:42,310
Please leave in an orderly fashion.

610
00:37:47,070 --> 00:37:48,790
Gather around!

611
00:37:49,150 --> 00:37:51,510
Follow my flag, and do not fall behind!

612
00:37:52,190 --> 00:37:53,190
Let's go.

613
00:37:53,270 --> 00:37:54,270
Go?

614
00:37:54,310 --> 00:37:55,390
If we go out now,

615
00:37:55,390 --> 00:37:56,950
we'll be killed by the needles!

616
00:37:56,950 --> 00:37:59,510
The tour guide is standing outside, safe and sound.

617
00:37:59,510 --> 00:38:01,670
A man just died. We can't stay here

618
00:38:02,710 --> 00:38:04,970
and spend the night at this place, can we?

619
00:38:14,320 --> 00:38:15,830
Gather around!

620
00:38:16,150 --> 00:38:18,350
Follow my flag, and do not fall behind.

621
00:38:27,270 --> 00:38:28,400
Everyone's here now, right?

622
00:38:28,400 --> 00:38:30,400
We need to go back before nightfall.

623
00:38:31,270 --> 00:38:33,710
How was your tour?
